snippet.title: Shoulders Of Giants - Now available for Pre-Order!
snippet.description:
Shoulders of Giants, a rougelike frog-and-robot adventure is coming out on January 26th, with a significant discount and bonus cosmetics for those who pre-purchase the game! For more info and to wishlist visit - https://www.movingpieces.io/sog

The soundtrack to the game was created by Tomas Dvorak aka Floex (Samorost, Machinarium). It will be available soon here - https://lnk.to/sog-ost
